      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just hard to see it as \"dangerous\" when it's the only thing that makes sense right now. everything is so loud and demanding, and the thought of just... fading out... is the only thing that feels quiet. like i'm not a person, i'm just an error that needs to be cleared so things can go back to normal. wouldn't it just be easier for everyone if things were just quiet?",
